<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <img src="images/blucollar-logo-non-bold.png" alt="Logo" />
    <p>Hello <%= @employer.name %>,</p>
    <p>
      We have some exciting news! A candidate has applied for the <a href= <%= @job.title %>> </a> position. Feel free to reach out to them to set up an interview.
    </p>
      <div class="candidate">
        <h3><%= @candidate.name %></h3>
        <p><%= @candidate.email %></p>
        <p><%= @candidate.address %></p>
      </div>
    <p>

      To login to the site, just follow this link: <a href=<%= @url %>>BluCollar</a>.
    </p>
    <p>Happy hunting and have a great day!</p>
    <p>BluCollar</p>
  </body>
</html>